            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This implies that &lt;code&gt;POST&lt;/code&gt; is likely to be sufficient for submitting a file via a form and that adding &lt;code&gt;multipart/form-data&lt;/code&gt; is just a bonus in some vague way. That&apos;s not the case. Most files will absolutely require using &lt;code&gt;multipart/form-data&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

